Ranger Help for: make trophy
=============================

SYNTAX:      mount corpse
             make trophy
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     20
SKILL TYPE:  survival

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to mount a trophy from a slain creature's
corpse. The trophy serves as a decoration and proof of the Ranger's
hunting prowess. The Ranger must have a corpse present in the room to
create the trophy. Different creatures produce different trophies. The
quality of the trophy depends on the Ranger's skill level. Trophies
can be displayed or carried as mementos of notable kills.
